We are glad to announce the revival of Google Developer Group (GDG) of Chisinau!

We are organizing the first GDG meetup in 2019 on 12th of April at 5:30pm at iHUB.

Our speakers are developers who work with Google technologies. They will share their knowledge and experience with us.

* Andrew Tomash - "Android Q. Is there a light at the end of the tunnel?"
* Vitalie Doni - "Billing for Small Business using Google Apps Script"

Also, after the event we will be enjoying beer and snacks with Silicon Drinkabout community at 7:00pm.

Join us!

The participation at the event is free (includng after-party), but the number of seats is limited. Please register here!

Disclaimer: GDG Chisinau is an independent group; our activities and the opinions expressed here should in no way be linked to Google, the corporation. To learn more about the GDG program, visit https://developers.google.com/groups/
